Description: Provides tools for evaluating and ranking missing
    data imputation methods using proper scoring rules.
    Implements the energy-I-Score from Näf et al. (2025)
    <doi:10.48550/arXiv.2507.11297> and the DR-I-Score
    introduced in Näf et al. (2022)
    <doi:10.48550/arXiv.2106.03742>.
    Supports deterministic, stochastic and multiple
    imputation methods for numerical and mixed datasets.
